Description: This sgroupr package is built to use some of the finite abelian groups. 
    You can find more information through this link: https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/List_of_small_groups.
    There are total 20 different groups that can be use in our sgroup package and 
    each group corresponds to one Cayley table.
